<li id="cite_note-SASDefinitions-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-SASDefinitions_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-SASDefinitions_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/weapons-and-markets/definitions.html">"Small Arms Survey: Definitions"</a>. <i>smallarmssurvey.org</i>. Small Arms Survey. April 15, 2013<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 10,</span> 2014</span>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGun+control&amp;rft.atitle=Small+Arms+Survey%3A+Definitions&amp;rft.date=April+15%2C+2013&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.smallarmssurvey.org%2Fweapons-and-markets%2Fdefinitions.html&amp;rft.jtitle=smallarmssurvey.org&amp;rft.pub=Small+Arms+Survey&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
